CatDescriptText: Cutline of related article published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, February 24, 1962, pg. 4 reads: "The Place...The Speakers! - Pictured above is Soldiers and Sailors Memorial hall, where Dr. James Nabrit (insert left), president of Howard University, and Bishop Joseph Gomez (insert, right) of the AME Church will headline a brilliant program at The Courier's Appreciation Day Rally this Sunday afternoon at 3 o'clock."
TitMainTitle: Man painting sign on window of Pittsburgh Courier newspaper printing plant, for Appreciation Day Rally with Dr. James Nabrit and Bishop G[omez] on Sunday Feb. 24th at Soldiers & Sailors Memorial Hall
